<title>Convertidor</title>
<p>This page explains all options for configuring the Converter in Preferences in <app>Parabolic</app>.</p>

<terms>
    <item>
        <title>Incrusta metadades</title>
        <p>Parabolic will tag a media with its relevant information (title, genre, etc...) if available.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Valor per defecte: activat</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Eliminar dades de font</title>
        <p>Parabolic will clear metadata fields containing identifying download information.</p>
        <p>Fields that are cleared: <code>comment</code>, <code>description</code>, <code>synopsis</code>, <code>purl</code> and <code>handler_name</code> in each stream.</p>
        <note>
            <p>This option is only configurable if <code>Embed Metadata</code> is on.</p>
        </note>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Valor per defecte: desactivat</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Incrusta miniatures</title>
        <p>Parabolic will embed a media with its thumbnail if available.</p>
        <p>Si el tipus de fitxer no suporta la incrustació, la miniatura s'escriurà a un fitxer d'imatge independent.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Valor per defecte: activat</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Retalla les miniatures d’àudio</title>
        <p>Parabolic will crop thumbnails of audio files to squares.</p>
        <note>
            <p>This option is only configurable if <code>Embed Thumbnails</code> is on.</p>
        </note>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Valor per defecte: desactivat</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Incrusta capítols</title>
        <p>Parabolic will tag a media with its chapter information if available.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Valor per defecte: desactivat</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Incrusta subtítols</title>
        <p>If disabled or if embedding is not supported, downloaded subtitles will be saved to separate files.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Valor per defecte: activat</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Postprocessing Threads</title>
        <p>Parabolic will limit the number of threads used by <code>ffmpeg</code>.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: The max number of threads available on the system</p>
        </note>
    </item>
</terms>
